0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"「警察面對劫匪暴徒汽油彈時，罷工嗎？消防員面對烈火熊熊時，罷工嗎？軍人面對強悍敵人時，罷工嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n如果政府無限供應武器，汽油彈俾劫匪暴徒，你作為警察，罷工嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果政府不斷派人到火場增添燃料，助燃劑，你作為消防員，罷工嗎？<br />\n<br />\n軍人面對強悍敵人，政府扣減軍費，只供給基本裝備，再將精良裝備派俾到隔離屋黃伯個仔，你作為軍人，罷工嗎？<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔會忘記 721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baac2cd6ab4c6bc778528efd0f055a657ff76535","tid":1860413,"uid":188,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hD4yTTR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhD4yTTR.png&h=f091751a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n弱智p牌 咪撚幫佢死鬼老母教仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30c2c7c113f37c0cb95cdd1c1a3b1c152645a26","tid":1860413,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79f265d791c6577cf717b6e6e448cb790cce2c0c","tid":1860413,"uid":84116,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"quote":{"pid":"767be04ba06897b67e81205f76cd6df055a7941b","tid":1860413,"uid":188,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢句野已經係支那傳黎傳去<br />\n話佢地幾日起好醫院 你地做逃兵<br />\n仲自私過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PG2D4QC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPG2D4QC.jpg&h=8feb9839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsend呢張相俾佢地睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets